'''Baron Cimitière''' (Baron Cemetery) is one of the [[Guédé]], a spirit of the dead, along with [[Baron Samedi]] and [[Baron La Croix]] in [[Haitian Vodun|Vodou]]. He is said to be the guardian of the cemetery, protecting its graves.<ref>http://horrorpedia.com/2013/10/15/baron-samedi-and-haitian-loa-folklore-religion/</ref>

He wears a tuxedo with tails and a top hat. He has expensive taste, smoking cigars and drinking wine and fine liquor. He is just as crass as the other Guédé, but shows polite manners and an upper-class air while doing so.

==Other manifestations==
Brave Guede is the doorman between the world of the living and the afterlife, guardian of the cemetery gate. He keeps the dead in and the living out.

