{{Politics of Liechtenstein}}
'''General elections''' were held in [[Liechtenstein]] on 1 September 1957.<ref name=NS>[[Dieter Nohlen]] & Philip Stöver (2010) ''Elections in Europe: A data handbook'', p1165 {{ISBN|978-3-8329-5609-7}}</ref> The [[Progressive Citizens' Party]] won eight of the 15 seats in the [[Landtag of Liechtenstein|Landtag]],<ref>Nohlen & Stöver, p1182</ref> but remained in coalition with the [[Patriotic Union (Liechtenstein)|Patriotic Union]].<ref>Nohlen & Stöver, p1157</ref>
